{"tid":2121159,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食環放生爆疫藍店 郭家麒轟執法不公","createTime":"2020-07-23T06:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T06:55:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e20e44527ed080166673bdbe06142b7730db63bc","tid":2121159,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/X26UAVGGP5ZELFWRBF7QGSXYO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FX26UAVGGP5ZELFWRBF7QGSXYO4%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCOCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=19396a8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FX26UAVGGP5ZELFWRBF7QGSXYO4%2F&h=a38271b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/X26UAVGGP5ZELFWRBF7QGSXYO4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n食環放生爆疫藍店 郭家麒轟執法不公<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XxsekbBEVeByJwdWpyJDCFIQMGc=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RR7PK27S37MULQCDS7O4DEAU5Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXxsekbBEVeByJwdWpyJDCFIQMGc%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRR7PK27S37MULQCDS7O4DEAU5Y.gif&h=9a2e5ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】第三波武漢肺炎疫情衍生出稻香、潮庭、富臨三大酒家感染群組，三間酒樓均涉嫌違反社交限制措施。不過，食環署只對最遲爆疫的富臨提出檢控，影片證明數百食客「除罩」跳舞唱歌的稻香、衞生防護中心曾指十多位賓客連患者「聚埋一齊」的美心潮庭，食環署仍未提控甚至調查。本身是醫生的立法會議員郭家麒（圖）狠批港府執法不公、刻意放生藍店酒家，「調轉係黃店，一早被處以極刑喇！」<br />\n<br />\n港府7月9日公佈兩日後開始再次收緊社交限制措施，當時食肆每枱人數沒有上限，但顧客在進食以外的時間須戴口罩，當日「中華輝煌會」在旺角稻香酒樓筵開近30席，網絡影片可見他們在進食以外的時間，脫下口罩又跳又唱，涉嫌違反法例。至7月。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，食環署至今未調查及檢控稻香及潮庭；反而張竹君從沒公佈「富臨群組」生日宴每枱人數為何，食環署就。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指淡化紀律部隊宿舍出事<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：共用廁所 隆亨院舍兩員工染疫<br />\n<br />\n郭認為，事件反映港府執法不公，樹立壞先例，更令公眾失去抗疫信心。尤其稻香的聚會有相片、影片為證，「一定違反法例，點解食環署唔檢控？係唔係藍店就可以為所欲為？」至於潮庭酒樓，郭稱公眾已知道患者。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n食環署表示，該署人員7月19日到旺角雅蘭中心稻香酒樓調查，發現該處所當日起關閉七天清潔消毒，由於該處所涉及確診群組，並可能有人涉嫌違反預防及控制疾病（規定及指示）（業務及處所）規例》（第599F章）。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"dff0dc976a5f9d548508c1ddbd42856faa0b9666","tid":2121159,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"繼續放生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成間唔要得架啦"},{"pid":"0d022fc947aa4a73e3584c47b05b2f9a0d2d6efd","tid":2121159,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ebd4603b222a764e97d499520e152a94383fec","tid":2121159,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:47:28.000Z","msg":"人地咁黃就唔好多聲氣啦<br />\n播毒都係比支那廢老同藍屍，少班支那狗"},{"pid":"20af787b637a87b823b77c31285729e93d1bd6d1","tid":2121159,"uid":230594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:47:51.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒<br />\n以前吸煙同小販都咁少拉人<br />\n指望佢哋真係蚊都瞓<br />\n一齊犯法都唔出奇"},{"pid":"0ab092a85f151b2d1055aa789e3763c0bc51a34a","tid":2121159,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20af787b637a87b823b77c31285729e93d1bd6d1","tid":2121159,"uid":230594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:47:51.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒<br />\n以前吸煙同小販都咁少拉人<br />\n指望佢哋真係蚊都瞓<br />\n一齊犯法都唔出奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"小販係只拉d跑唔到既阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}